    • Constructor Detail

      • TopNNames

        public TopNNames​(int startYear,
                 int endYear,
                 java.lang.String gender,
                 int numNames,
                 java.lang.String country,
                 java.lang.String type)
        This constructors main role is to set up the hashmaps so data can be pulled from them rapidly. It also sends information to the report logger so that information found here may be exported too.
        Parameters:
        startYear - from which year the user would like to start seeing the top N names.
        endYear - the last year the user would like to see the top N names for.
        gender - the gender the user is interested in.
        numNames - the number of names per year the user would like to see.
        country - the country of interest.
        type - the type of interest - almost guaranteed to be human.
